data.description: Located in Fairfield Sunrise Territory Village, this spacious 2bdr/2ba w/bonus room sits atop the ridge line with unobstructed views from the front and back!Enter through gated courtyard withWrap around covered patio offering fabulous outdoor seating and mountain/city views!Living room features wood burning fireplace, dining room overlooks the back patio,  primary bedroom offers patio access and roll down shutter. Ensuite w/garden tub, separate shower, dual vanity and huge double door walk-in closet.2nd bedroom has private patio for evening sunsets!Community pool and spa at end of cul de sac.HVAC replaced in 2016 and new hot water heater in 2020.
